description: WHAT IS CHEF TAI’S MOBILE GOURMET?Chef Tai’s Mobile Gourmet, AMERICA'S FAVORITE FOOD TRUCK according to Food Network, serves Chef Tai’s unique blend of Globally inspired cuisine from a mobile kitchen in essence, a recreation of the kitchen from Veritas Wine & Bistro.As a Texas A&M; University Graduate, Chef Tai felt a strong need to create something that is unique to Aggieland and budget friendly.A fun and inexpensive alternative to an upscale dinning experience, Chef Tai’s Globally inspired menu includes: BBQ Pulled Pork Tacos, Korean Short Rib BBQ Bowl, and Brussels Tofu Florentine all priced under $8. Under the direction of Chef Tai Lee, we have developed a menu that delivers high-end food at street level prices.We look forward to meeting you throughout the streets of Bryan and College Station.Please stop by and say HOWDY!HAVING A PARTY?You can have your very own Chef Tai’s Mobile Gourmet Truck roll up to your festivities.
name: Chef Tai's Mobile Bistro
